name: Dropbox
SQL: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `dropbox`(`id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,`name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,`key` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,`userid` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,`status` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,`timestamp` TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,PRIMARY KEY (`id`),UNIQUE KEY `userid` (`userid`)) ENGINE=InnoDB  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=20
